    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="关于我"><a href="#关于我" class="headerlink" title="关于我"></a>关于我</h3><p>​1、曾就职于深信服深蓝实验室攻防研究部，深信服华中天慧攻防战队。多次省级护网前二，10+实战攻防项目，100+漏洞挖掘项目</p><p>​2、漏洞盒子总榜第四十六名、漏洞盒子在2020年7月份之前，获得10+个月的月榜前十、漏洞盒子2020年第三赛季总榜第四十二名</p><p>​3、补天积分总榜前七百名，补天漏洞数量总榜第四十名、2019年12月补天战神、补天双旦活动获得丰厚双旦过节基金、补天五一活动获得冰箱奖励</p><p>​4、去哪网SRC总榜第八十四名</p><p>​5、多项CTF比赛及多个CTF平台排名靠前</p><p>​6、总计为世界、国家及各大SRC平台和社区提交5000+有效漏洞</p><p>​7、多次获得CVE编号、CNVD证书</p><figure class="highlight subunit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs subunit">CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46046</span>、CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46047</span>、CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46048</span>、CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46049</span>、CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46050</span><br>CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46051</span>、CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46052</span>、CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46053</span>、CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46055</span>、CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46056</span><br>CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46057</span>、CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46058</span>、CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46059</span>、CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46061</span>、CVE<span class="hljs-string">-2022</span><span class="hljs-string">-46062</span><br>CVE<span class="hljs-s